# The npm-workspaces root package-lock.json is the ONLY lockfile.
# A stray nested one is never consulted by installs or the Docker
# builds, but Dependabot still scans it — a stale copy once raised
# phantom vulnerability alerts for long-since-patched versions.
apps/*/package-lock.json
packages/*/package-lock.json

# Claude Code local scratch — worktrees for isolated parallel agents,
# session metadata. Never federated, never published.
.claude/
